sign~
Hello,for those who are wondering, this area was originally intended for the
amusement of the players, however, since it has expanded beyond just the inn
(as you shall no doubt find out) its become an xp area.
 
This area consists of mobs varying from DayCare Mobs to Atlantis level mobs
(some even tougher). This obviously means there are some pretty mean mobs in
here, newbies are NOT suggested in the exp area but are suggested to explore
the inn section of the area. Most of the mobs are aggressive and pack a
punch..so watch out!

For those more experienced players, explore, exploit and most of all, have fun.

                                    - MereK
~
