#15244
Dedication...~
Just as a note to whom ever finds this room... This was my first (completed)
attempt at building, many hours have gone into this area and no doubt many
more will.

I would just like to thank a few people who brought me into the mudding world.
Dragonsworn, Danyn and Synner, who first introduced me to mudding at school
and to the awsome mud named Diamondgate. Sancho, Epoch and Weasel who i met
on my first mud and have kept in contact since. I've met alot of interesting
and special people during the 5 or 6 years i've been mudding. Some know me as
Merek, some as MoonwicK, and some who are unaware that they know me at all and
probably i shall never tell them for the sake of role playing and i would'nt
want to shock them too much.

Most of all i would like to thank Aria, my angel and financee rl whom i met
online, may our love extend the boundries of time and beyond. 

Aria, my love....I dedicate my first area to you.

                                           - MereK/MoonwicK  18/12/99

~
